五毛周圍散播失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔做一樣野唔洗開大聲公同人講</blockquote><br />\n喂屌而家班撚樣call行哂馬出去但完全係廢up幾句散場<br />\n係咪唔可以屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd20603a394de229459923980bdabe943029b4e","tid":321731,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"係咪要做天真無邪小朋友永遠支持飯民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bebe2290cceb6729ac8e6a3f2ab5a4c0fa4b80","tid":321731,"uid":34144,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你真係有出到去你就會明點解會心淡</blockquote><br />\n我出撚左去但唔覺心淡喎,泛民嘅和理非見人數唔夠,點可能會做野?你試下有十萬人,泛民想叫散水有咁撚易? 根本係惡性循環, 一班人叫集會唔衝-&gt;不了-&gt;少人-&gt;更加唔衝-&gt;更加不了。<br />\n<br />\n最後咪做撚左689條金魚。<br />\n<br />\n胡椒食過,龍和道果陣俾泛民大台出賣過,唔撚會信佢地,但私怨還私怨,呢啲場合點都要睇下有冇機會。人太少咪散,夠人咪睇下有冇行動。"},{"pid":"e72c10b8761478abeef29cc9d092e74642b0c03c","tid":321731,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"最小百幾隻齊齊發功，先主導頭幾個貼，之後就有班小學雞跟瘋幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ed6f8b6565e5c2f848df38522168b6caf22796","tid":321731,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最小百幾隻齊齊發功，先主導頭幾個貼，之後就有班小學雞跟瘋幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有o的一唱一和"},{"pid":"20348f7d6faf2f9705872e37031a5f8af79de9f1","tid":321731,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:05:36.000Z","msg":"已經有幾隻五毛入左黎開工"},{"pid":"9e2e4ee4da07ba733b827fa02d3b4d1303779430","tid":321731,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2170c1802b0292334c9d5cd59cad598fc86814b","tid":321731,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply